{"tid":115382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狂男車廂大叫：你班仆街　燒死你哋","createTime":"2017-02-10T13:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T16:39:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4978e24eca53f8d69bc588d3087224d35ee21ed0","tid":115382,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"【21：15更新】更新內容【20：40更新】懷疑在車廂內投擲汽油彈的男疑人，身上有三級燒傷，他身上沒有任何證明文件，由警員押送往醫院治理傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n狂男在港鐵車廂縱火事件，據最新消息稱，狂男年約40歲，事後他被警方拘捕，並向警方揚言在車廂內自焚自殺。警方正循縱火方向調查。<br />\n<br />\n據知，狂男當時在車廂內站在車門旁邊，突然自言自語：「你班仆街，燒死你哋！」亦有大聽到他說「個仔被人害死」，其後狂男拿着一個玻璃酒樽，將樽內的液體照頭淋，隨後點火，狂男瞬間變成火人，旁邊的乘客亦首當其衝，不少乘客被燒傷，車廂頓時變煉獄。"},{"pid":"a402de65ee495ab517d1fe52a08a8e1c0644cb4c","tid":115382,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170210&amp;guid=56288293&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170210%26guid%3D56288293%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d462c9f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170210%26guid%3D56288293%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=5926bd05\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170210&amp;guid=56288293&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"1f9ad74dd9506617d172a9670bca32d75efa25e9","tid":115382,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"當時企佢身邊啲人點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea95621991d35c311b513c182ebfe8dc925224e","tid":115382,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc34c96ded